-- Custodian and Allied Insurance of Nigeria First-Half Profit Advances 42%
-- Vernon Wessels
-- 2010-07-30T10:21:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/custodian-and-allied-insurance-of-nigeria-first-half-profit-advances-42-.html

          
          
             Custodian and Allied Insurance Plc
said first-half profit rose to 1.21 billion naira from 851.6
million naira a year earlier, according to a statement e-mailed
by the Lagos-based Nigerian Stock Exchange today.  
 Sales surged to 4.4 billion naira from 2.9 billion naira a
year earlier, it said.  
          
          


  


        